,"         MaxPool2d-2           [-1, 32, 48, 48]               0\n","              ReLU-3           [-1, 32, 48, 48]               0\n","         Dropout2d-4           [-1, 32, 48, 48]               0\n","       BatchNorm2d-5           [-1, 32, 48, 48]              64\n","            Conv2d-6           [-1, 64, 48, 48]          18,496\n","         MaxPool2d-7           [-1, 64, 24, 24]               0\n","              ReLU-8           [-1, 64, 24, 24]               0\n","         Dropout2d-9           [-1, 64, 24, 24]               0\n","      BatchNorm2d-10           [-1, 64, 24, 24]             128\n","           Conv2d-11          [-1, 128, 24, 24]          73,856\n","        MaxPool2d-12          [-1, 128, 12, 12]               0\n","             ReLU-13          [-1, 128, 12, 12]               0\n","        Dropout2d-14          [-1, 128, 12, 12]               0\n","      BatchNorm2d-15          [-1, 128, 12, 12]             256\n","           Conv2d-16          [-1, 128, 12, 12]         147,584\n","        MaxPool2d-17            [-1, 128, 6, 6]               0\n","             ReLU-18            [-1, 128, 6, 6]               0\n","        Dropout2d-19            [-1, 128, 6, 6]               0\n","      BatchNorm2d-20            [-1, 128, 6, 6]             256\n","          Flatten-21                 [-1, 4608]               0\n","      BatchNorm1d-22                 [-1, 4608]           9,216\n","           Linear-23                  [-1, 256]       1,179,904\n","             ReLU-24                  [-1, 256]               0\n","          Dropout-25                  [-1, 256]               0\n","      BatchNorm1d-26                  [-1, 256]             512\n","           Linear-27                    [-1, 2]             514\n","          Sigmoid-28                    [-1, 2]               0\n","================================================================\n","Total params: 1,431,682\n","Trainable params: 1,431,682\n","Non-trainable params: 0\n","----------------------------------------------------------------\n","Input size (MB): 0.11\n","Forward/backward pass size (MB): 8.23\n","Params size (MB): 5.46\n","Estimated Total Size (MB): 13.80\n","----------------------------------------------------------------\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## Давайте посмотрим на предсказания нашей сети.\n","\n","Сделаем функцию, которая визуализирует предсказания на валидационном даталоадере.\n","Вызовите эту функцию несколько раз и посмотрите на результаты работы."],"metadata":{"id":"xfdECAx62jyy"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["import random\n","\n","def plot_predict_from_loader(loader, model):\n","    data_batch, label_batch = next(iter(loader))\n","    with torch.inference_mode(): # В режиме инференса предсказываем наш батч.\n","    # В этом режиме модель не тратит вычислительные ресурсы на подсчет градиентов на валидации.\n","    # Поскольку на валидации веса мы обновлять не планируем - это ускоряет работу модели.\n","        logits = model(data_batch.to(device))\n","        y_pred = logits.max(1)[1].data\n","        y_pred = y_pred.detach().cpu().numpy()\n","    grid_size = (3, 3)\n","    f, axarr = plt.subplots(*grid_size)\n","    f.set_size_inches(15,10)\n","    class_names = loader.dataset.classes\n","    for grid_num, i in enumerate(range(grid_size[0] * grid_size[1])):\n","        i = random.randint(0, BATCH_SIZE - 1)\n","        # read images from batch to numpy.ndarray and change axes order [H, W, C] -> [H, W, C]\n","        batch_image_ndarray = np.transpose(data_batch[i].numpy(), [1, 2, 0])\n","\n","        # inverse normalization for image data values back to [0,1] and clipping the values for correct pyplot.imshow()\n","        src = np.clip(image_std * batch_image_ndarray + image_mean, 0, 1)\n","\n","        # display batch samples with labels\n","        sample_title = f'''Label = {label_batch[i]} ({class_names[label_batch[i]]}), Prediction: {y_pred[i]} ({class_names[y_pred[i]]})'''\n","        axarr[grid_num // grid_size[0], grid_num % grid_size[0]].imshow(src)\n","        axarr[grid_num // grid_size[0], grid_num % grid_size[0]].set_title(sample_title)"],"metadata":{"id":"GD6NK2E70t1G","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772635003276,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":10,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"execution_count":61,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["plot_predict_from_loader(val_loader, model_cnn)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":389},"id":"X9rOMyl61dgn","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772635009068,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":2305,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}},"outputId":"47fc3785-f133-49e0-85ba-ab0a9888f23d"},"execution_count":62,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1500x1000 with 9 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"C69Gtezv9PS9"},"source":["#### Training"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"6GSpqx2KrQfM"},"source":["**Напоминаем ещё раз:** не ждите слишком много эпох. Вы можете прервать обучение после 5 - 20 эпох, как только точность на валидации перестанет расти."]},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"FCONrVDoJyPm"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]}]}